caption:
WOW. ❤️ I’m incredibly honored (and still a little blown away) to share that I’ve been named a 2024 @Entreprenista100 Award Winner!!

The Entreprenista 100 award honors 100 exemplary business owners each year. To be recognized alongside 99 other powerhouse women building bold, meaningful businesses? It’s surreal—and deeply humbling. It is also a powerful reminder that community matters, the work we’re doing makes an impact, and yes—we absolutely can build businesses on our own terms!

I didn’t start this entrepreneurial journey for recognition. I set out to make a difference—to help women safeguard their dreams, and to show my boys what it looks like to stay the course when things get hard, to believe in yourself when it counts most, and to lead with both courage and conviction.

Thank you to @Entreprenista, @stephjillcartin and @courtspritzer for this incredible honor. And thank you to every client, colleague, and friend who has been part of this journey with me. I wouldn’t be here without you, and I’m forever grateful! 😍

Here’s to showing up, lifting each other up, and continuing to build with heart. Let’s write this next chapter together!
